*What you will build
No more looking around the table to see who's taking care of the tip with this calculator.
* file used html,css for styleing  and javascript for operations
*Javascript used
DOM manipulation
Functions
timers to display contains
alert message  for amount checking 

*Takeaway and thoughts
Writing the function that determines the amount each person will tip was rather easy.
 Perhaps the greatest challenge here was using CSS to mimic the design of the app. 
 It looks like a rather simple design but it's actually a little challenging to do without watching the tutorial first.
 